messages.message:
Need to make some changes to our build logic
https://aihub-sandbox.internal.instabase.com/build/01993206-c422-7024-b47b-8dbba7422008

Half the fields are erroring out. My guess is hit the field count limit. @Abhishek Adupa added logic to support large number of fields in app runs.
Related: we should probably move back to per field with option to re-run all fields.
Every time we add a field, it is triggering a flash-extraction for all fields
https://aihub-sandbox.internal.instabase.com/api/v2/aihub/build/projects/01993206-c422-7024-b47b-8dbba7422008/flash-extraction - this can be quite slow.

cc @pauline.comising
